me.com/news/music/ed-sheeran-announces-second-new-album-of-2023-autumn-variations-3488184">《Autumn Variations》</a> 。本周早些时候，他透露， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ed-sheeran-secretly-recorded-live-version-of-new-album-autumn-variations-in-fans-homes-3501006">他录制了即将发行的专辑的现场版本</a>，让歌迷们惊喜不已，并在他们的家里表演。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/j-balvin-and-ed-sheeran-set-to-drop-joint-album-next-year-3501065">J Balvin 和 Ed Sheeran 将于明年推出联合专辑的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
